&lt;p&gt;As an&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Overnight Trader&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;on our FICC team, you’ll have an opportunity to combine the disciplines of risk management, research and technology to develop and execute innovative trading strategies in some of the world’s most competitive markets. Teams are close-knit groups and will allow new traders to grow into a key role within the team without a prolonged training period by trading overnight. If you’re looking for responsibility and the opportunity to have an impact on a desk, this is the role for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;*Please note - this role is based in the Singapore office, and covers the US trading hours of 11pm to 8am.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
